!! Config tiddler fields

|!Field |!Type |!Description |
|`rri.type` |string |Must be `explide/config` to trigger the IDE |
|`rri.imported-plugins` |space-separated list |Plugin titles to import into the sandbox |
|`rri.imported-tiddlers` |space-separated list |Individual tiddler titles to import |
|`rri.output-tiddler` |string |Title of the testcase output tiddler (default: `Output`) |
|`description` |string |Description shown in the testcase header |
|`rri.adhoc-tiddler:<name>` |string |Inline text-only tiddler content (name becomes the sandbox title) |

!! Explide data tiddler convention

When a shadow tiddler is added from an imported plugin, a data tiddler is created at:

```
<configTitle>/<shadowTiddlerTitle>
```

!! `$rri$:` field prefix

Fields on data tiddlers prefixed with `$rri$:` are remapped in the sandbox:

|!Data tiddler field |!Sandbox field |
|`$rri$:tags` |`tags` |
|`$rri$:type` |`type` |
|`$rri$:<fieldname>` |`<fieldname>` |

Regular fields (except `title`) pass through unchanged.

!! Filter functions (`variables.tid`)

|!Function |!Purpose |
|`rri.explide-data(config)` |Lists all explide data tiddlers for a config (children minus snapshots) |
|`rri.explide-tiddlers(config)` |Explide data titles with config prefix stripped (original names) |
|`rri.imported-tiddlers(config)` |Lists individually imported tiddler titles from `rri.imported-tiddlers` field |
|`rri.get-source-data(config, data)` |Computes original tiddler name from a data tiddler title |
|`rri.get-snapshot-data(config, data)` |Resolves snapshot tiddler or falls back to original |
|`rri.is-plugin-imported(config, plugin)` |Checks if a plugin is in the imported list |
|`rri.is-any-plugin-member-used(config, plugin)` |Checks if any shadow tiddler from a plugin is used as explide data |
|`rri.is-plugin-involved(config, plugin)` |Checks if a plugin is imported or has used shadow tiddlers |

!! IDE tabs

|!Tab |!Content |
|CONFIG |Plugin import toggles, shadow tiddler browser, bulk import |
|ADHOC |Ad-hoc tiddler editor (create/edit/delete inline tiddlers) |
|DIAGNOSTICS |Missing plugins, missing tiddlers, unused imports, stale snapshots |
|`<data title>` |One tab per explide data tiddler — EDITOR, FIELDS, DIFF sub-tabs |

